<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>英语学习 - 音形义分离法</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-brand">英语学习</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="index.html" class="active">首页</a>
            <a href="learn.html">学习</a>
            <a href="profile.html">我的</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>音形义分离学习法</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">见词能读，听音能写，先音形，后释义</p>
            <div class="cta-group">
                <a href="learn.html" class="btn btn-primary">开始学习</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">了解方法</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <h2>为什么选择音形义分离？</h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>降低认知负荷</h3>
                    <p>一次只学2样（音+形），比传统方法（音+形+义）更容易掌握</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
                    <h3>科学学习路径</h3>
                    <p>第一阶段建立音形基础，第二阶段理解含义，循序渐进</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
                    <h3>英语思维培养</h3>
                    <p>用英英释义理解单词，避免中文翻译的中介</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="how-it-works">
            <h2>学习流程</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <h3>第一阶段：音形训练</h3>
                    <p>只记拼写和发音，不记意思。看到词就能读，听到词就能写。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h3>第二阶段：英英释义</h3>
                    <p>用简单词解释复杂词，建立英语思维，深入理解含义。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h3>综合应用</h3>
                    <p>音形义结合，在真实语境中运用，真正掌握单词。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="stats">
            <h2>学习数据</h2>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">已学单词</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">学习天数</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">0%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">准确率</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 英语学习 - 音形义分离法</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/error-handler.js"></script>
    <script src="js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
